title: 11/09/2020 - Best of The Herd

description:
-Colin has no idea what the Bucs were even trying to do against the Saints

-Tua is perfectly built for this Dolphins team

-Russell Wilson is pressing because he knows he has to do everything

-The Steelers still don't look like a team you can trust

-Where Colin was right, where Colin was wrong


Guest: Jimmy Johnson, 2x Super Bowl Champion & NFL on FOX
